123
00:09:08,674 --> 00:09:10,133
Potrei farti il tuo profilo se vuoi.

124
00:09:12,135 --> 00:09:12,928
O no.

125
00:09:15,055 --> 00:09:16,098
Gemelli.

126
00:09:21,353 --> 00:09:22,688
Hey, Jack.

127
00:09:24,648 --> 00:09:25,399
Whoa.

128
00:09:27,109 --> 00:09:28,277
Sembri stanco, fratello.

129
00:09:29,736 --> 00:09:30,571
Sto bene.

130
